<heading>list - List all contacts.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>list</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Lists all contacts with their name and company.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>list
  List all contacts.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>add, delete, edit, find, show</paragraph>
